  "description": "This individual presents as an animated cadaver of human origin, with taut pale skinTone stretched over prominent bone and a persistent ash-dust patina typical of long exposure to fissure air. Brown eyes sit deep within darkened sockets, and brown hair hangs in a sparse, uneven fall that exposes scalp in irregular patches. The jawline is slightly misaligned, and the mouth shows blackened gums and broken teeth consistent with post-mortem desiccation and fracture. Movement is deliberate and mechanical, marked by rigid joints and a fixed forward stare characteristic of the Ashglass Fissure dead.",
